These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, scientific
3 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, rabbit
1. the person watching adventure movies is the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | scientific | mystery    |
| Pet     | frog    | rabbit       | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, librarian, pilot
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, iced-tea
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the pilot is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
4. the librarian is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | pilot | fisherman | librarian  |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | mirinda  | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, paramedic, videographer
House: cottage, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the accountant is on the far right##1
3. the paramedic is the colonial house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the colonial house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | videographer | paramedic | accountant |
| House   | cottage        | colonial    | gothic-revival        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, cape-coding, video-games
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, cottage
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cape-coding##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cape-coding##3
3. the cape-cod house is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | cape-coding | baking |
| House     | farmhouse  | cape-cod    | cottage  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, juice
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, subway, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | lemonade | juice |
| Transport     | subway   | ship   | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, folk, gospel
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, engineer, lawyer
1. the lawyer is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
4. the fan of house is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house | folk      |
| Job     | engineer  | lawyer | accountant |

