.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, western, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, dutch, malaysian
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | animation    | spy       |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian | australian |

