.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
City: miami, new-york, london
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, techno
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| City           | miami | new-york | london |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco | r&b     |

