.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, water
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, mauve, ivory
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
2. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite    | water      |
| Color   | mauve       | coral | ivory |

