.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, water
House: farmhouse, wooden, ranch-style
1. the farmhouse house is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking tea##2
2. the wooden house is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | tea    | water    | sprite  |
| House   | wooden | farmhouse | ranch-style |

