.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, malaysian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, aconite
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left or far right##3
2. the malaysian is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who growsaconite is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsamaryllis##2
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | american | malaysian | colombian |
| Flower           | marigold    | aconite    | amaryllis       |

