3. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate |
