.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower, corn
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, mah-jongg
1. the person eating cabbage is the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
3. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Food          | cauliflower | corn    | cabbage |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | snooker | whist  |

